## âš™ï¸ **STEP 6: CREATE CONFIGURATION FILE**

In the `config` folder, create `application.properties`:

```properties
# Database Configuration
database.url=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/marketplace_db
database.username=postgres
database.password=postgres

# RabbitMQ Configuration
rabbitmq.host=localhost
rabbitmq.port=5672
rabbitmq.username=guest
rabbitmq.password=guest

# Saga Queues
rabbitmq.queue.saga.commands=saga.commands.queue
rabbitmq.queue.compensation.commands=compensation.commands.queue

# Server Port
server.port=8082

# Logging
logging.level.com.university.marketplace=DEBUG
